{
    "description_long": "This object is a small graveyard cluster featuring seven distinct grave markers arranged in a circular pattern on a dark, flat base. The markers include a variety of headstones and crosses, each with unique shapes and weathered textures, suggesting age and exposure to the elements. Most of the grave markers are made of stone, with some showing reddish-brown hues indicative of iron or rusted metal details. The crosses vary in style, including both simple Latin and more ornate forms, and some headstones have curved or angled tops. The surfaces are rough and matte, with visible chips and erosion, adding to the sense of realism and antiquity. No visible inscriptions or text are present on the grave markers, and there are no mausoleums or gates included in this arrangement.",
    "description": "A small, weathered graveyard cluster with seven stone grave markers and crosses arranged on a dark circular base, featuring rough, aged surfaces and varied shapes.",
